      "value": "As a Data Scientist holding a Master's from the University of Maryland, I bring specialized expertise in Generative AI, LLM systems, and Machine Learning, with a proven track record in developing and deploying innovative AI solutions. My work includes architecting an AI-Assisted Job Application Automation Platform that processed over 650 applications, reducing application time by 87%, and developing Mimikree, a personalized AI assistant featuring an adaptive RAG pipeline and containerized microservices.\n\nI am adept with LangChain, HuggingFace, PyTorch, AWS, Docker, and advanced alignment techniques like DPO and QLoRA, as demonstrated in my Domain-Aligned Speculative Decoding research. Eager to contribute immediately, I am keen to apply my full-stack AI and cloud capabilities to drive impactful projects and achieve significant results.",
